select count(*) from odw_standardised_db.dbo.document_meta_data 
WHERE ingested_datetime=(select max(ingested_datetime) from odw_standardised_db.dbo.document_meta_data )

select dataid, name, version, count(*)
from odw_standardised_db.dbo.document_meta_data 
where expected_from=(select max(expected_from) from [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[document_meta_data])
group by dataid, name,version
having count(*) > 1


select *
from odw_standardised_db.dbo.horizon_appeals_document_metadata 
where expected_from=(select max(expected_from) from [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[horizon_appeals_document_metadata])
and documentid=10843465


select  documentId, filename, count(*)
from odw_standardised_db.dbo.horizon_appeals_document_metadata 
where ingested_datetime=(select max(ingested_datetime) from [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[horizon_appeals_document_metadata])
group by documentId, filename,version
having count(*) > 1

select dataid, expected_from, count(*)

from odw_standardised_db.dbo.document_meta_data 
group by dataid, expected_from
having count(*) > 1


select top 10 * from odw_standardised_db.dbo.document_meta_data
where dataid in (
    SELECT distinct documentid FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[aie_document_data]
) and expected_from=(select max(expected_from) from [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[document_meta_data])
